<ab><expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Plassemberg<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> zu
                        Peyrrewt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch
                                <expan>fürkome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, daz Cönczlin ewr knecht in
                                <expan>schulde<ex>n</ex></expan> gen uns süll sein von der hab
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>aufgeslage<ex>n</ex></expan> ward, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> er
                        geleyts zu uns begert sich <expan>zu v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>
                        etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und wenn
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Cönczlin in xiiii
                            <expan>tage<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>nehste<ex>n</ex></expan> zu uns
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> meynt zu
                            <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, so sol er umb
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> zu uns, von uns, für uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on geverd drey tag geleyt
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        sein red <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören. Denn wo wir ewch lieb
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
